WEBVTT

00:01.042 --> 00:02.419
AH-HYUCK.

00:02.419 --> 00:04.629
♪ H-H-H-HIT IT ♪

00:04.629 --> 00:06.798
♪ LIKE FATHER, LIKE SON ♪

00:06.798 --> 00:09.175
♪ YOU'RE ALWAYS NUMBER ONE ♪
YES!

00:09.175 --> 00:12.095
♪ BEST BUDDIES, BEST PALS ♪
♪ YEAH ♪

00:12.095 --> 00:14.097
♪ YOU ALWAYS SEEM
TO WORK THINGS OUT ♪

00:14.097 --> 00:16.391
♪ CAN'T YOU SEE
YOU'RE TWO OF A KIND ♪

00:16.391 --> 00:18.810
♪ LOOKIN' FOR
A REAL GOOD TIME? ♪

00:18.810 --> 00:20.437
WHAA-OOO-HO-HO!

00:20.437 --> 00:22.105
♪ A REAL GOOD TIME ♪

00:22.105 --> 00:24.107
♪ REPORT
TO THE GOOF TROOP ♪

00:24.107 --> 00:25.775
♪ AND WE'LL ALWAYS
STICK TOGETHER ♪

00:25.775 --> 00:27.777
♪ ALWAYS
STICK TOGETHER ♪

00:27.777 --> 00:29.404
♪ WE'RE THE GOOF TROOP ♪

00:29.404 --> 00:31.656
♪ THE BEST OF FRIENDS
FOREVER ♪

00:33.116 --> 00:35.243
♪ SIDE BY SIDE
WHEREVER WE GO ♪

00:35.243 --> 00:39.622
♪ WE'RE ALWAYS READY TO ROLL ♪

00:39.622 --> 00:41.249
♪ NOW GIMME A BEAT ♪

00:41.249 --> 00:42.584
♪ WE'RE THE GOOF TROOP ♪

00:42.584 --> 00:45.587
♪ AND WE ALWAYS
STICK TOGETHER ♪

00:45.587 --> 00:47.589
GAWRSH.
♪ WE'RE THE GOOF TROOP ♪

00:47.589 --> 00:51.468
♪ THE BEST OF FRIENDS
FOREVER ♪

00:51.468 --> 00:53.845
♪ NOW WE'RE CALLING
EVERYONE ♪

00:53.845 --> 00:55.680
♪ COME ALONG
AND JOIN THE FUN ♪

00:55.680 --> 00:57.432
♪ REPORT TO
THE GOOF TROOP ♪

00:57.432 --> 00:58.767
♪ LA DO BE DA BOP
LA BA DO BOP ♪

00:58.767 --> 00:59.851
YEAH!

01:04.981 --> 01:07.317
[PJ] HAS ANYONE
SEEN MY BALL GLOVE?

01:07.317 --> 01:08.860
[GRRR]

01:34.969 --> 01:36.638
YO, PEEJ! YOU READY?

01:42.143 --> 01:44.521
AW, MAN! WHERE'D YOU GO?

01:44.521 --> 01:46.064
[DOOR SLAMS]

01:46.064 --> 01:47.482
[GRUMBLING]

01:47.482 --> 01:49.234
YO, MR. P!

01:49.234 --> 01:51.861
Yo, Mr. P.

01:51.861 --> 01:54.489
SHAKE IT, PETE,
BEFORE IT GETS TOO DARK.

01:54.489 --> 01:56.658
I CAN'T FIND
MY GLOVE.

01:56.658 --> 01:58.326
HAVE YOU LOOKED UNDER HERE?

01:58.326 --> 02:01.871
LISTEN, YOU TWO.
THIS IS MY DAY OFF.

02:01.871 --> 02:05.500
ALL I WANT TO DO IS RELAX
AND READ MY NEWSPAPER

02:05.500 --> 02:07.460
WITH A LITTLE
PEACE AND QUIET!

02:07.460 --> 02:10.338
UH, N-NO SWEAT, MR. P.
NOT ANOTHER SOUND.

02:10.338 --> 02:12.215
QUIET AS MICE, STILL
AS A TOMB, PEACEFUL AS--

02:12.215 --> 02:13.633
PIPE DOWN!

02:15.635 --> 02:17.429
SHH!

02:21.433 --> 02:23.018
[GRRR]

02:25.520 --> 02:29.065
OH, MAN, I GIVE UP.
IT'S GONE.

02:29.065 --> 02:30.900
SOMEBODY MUST'VE
STOLEN IT.

02:30.900 --> 02:34.070
RIGHT, PEEJ. LIKE BURGLARS
BROKE IN YOUR HOUSE

02:34.070 --> 02:35.447
TO SNATCH A BALL GLOVE.

02:35.447 --> 02:41.244
HMM. YOU KNOW, MAX,
PJ HAS A POINT.

02:41.244 --> 02:43.163
LOOKY HERE.

02:43.163 --> 02:45.623
"HOME BURGLARIES
ON THE RISE.

02:45.623 --> 02:49.836
SOON, ONE HOME
IN FOUR WILL BE ROBBED."

02:49.836 --> 02:51.087
TOLD YA.

02:51.087 --> 02:53.465
YOU'RE JUMPIN' THE GUN, SON.

02:53.465 --> 02:57.427
THEY WON'T ROB US.
WE'RE NOT NUMBER FOUR.

02:57.427 --> 02:58.762
HUH?

02:58.762 --> 03:01.765
WELL, START DOWN THE BLOCK
AND COUNT.

03:01.765 --> 03:03.475
THE TAYLORS.
1.

03:03.475 --> 03:05.435
THE WILSONS.
2.

03:05.435 --> 03:07.437
MY HOUSE.
3.

03:07.437 --> 03:09.731
YOUR HOUSE.

03:09.731 --> 03:10.815
[GULP]

03:10.815 --> 03:12.609
OH, MY GOSH. MY HOUSE!

03:12.609 --> 03:15.820
WE'RE GONNA BE ROBBED!
WE'RE GONNA BE ROBBED!

03:15.820 --> 03:18.490
OH, QUICK, SON,
GO WARN YOUR DAD.

03:18.490 --> 03:23.161
HA HA HA HA! THAT GOT RID
OF THE LITTLE BEAN DIP.

03:24.579 --> 03:27.624
BURGLARS! ROBBERS!
THIEVES!

03:30.210 --> 03:32.295
[RATTLE]

03:34.506 --> 03:36.508
WHOA!

03:40.512 --> 03:43.807
WELL, IF THAT DON'T
BEAT ALL. AH-HYUCK!

03:43.807 --> 03:46.434
DAD! QUICK! LOCK THE CAT!
NAIL THE JEWELRY!

03:46.434 --> 03:47.769
AND HIDE THE DOOR CLOSED!

03:47.769 --> 03:50.814
SLOW DOWN, SON.
WHAT'S WRONG?

03:50.814 --> 03:52.315
WE'RE GONNA BE ROBBED!

03:52.315 --> 03:53.483
ROBBED?

03:53.483 --> 03:55.652
YEAH! WE'RE NUMBER FOUR!

03:55.652 --> 03:57.612
RELAX, MAX.

03:57.612 --> 03:59.030
WE'RE TOTALLY SAFE.

03:59.030 --> 04:00.824
NO. NO, WE'RE NOT.

04:00.824 --> 04:03.952
HECK. NO BURGLAR'S GONNA
BREAK INTO OUR HOME.

04:03.952 --> 04:06.037
WHY, IT'S UNBREAKABLE.

04:13.294 --> 04:14.754
YOU'RE NOT INSTILLING ME

04:14.754 --> 04:16.464
WITH TREMENDOUS
CONFIDENCE HERE, DAD.

04:16.464 --> 04:18.633
OKAY, THEN.
WATCH WHAT I DO

04:18.633 --> 04:20.218
EVERY NIGHT
BEFORE GOING TO BED.

04:20.218 --> 04:23.179
I DOUBLE-LOCK
ALL THE DOORS.

04:28.893 --> 04:32.188
NO CROOK COULD EVER
GET BY OLD WAFFLES HERE.

04:32.188 --> 04:35.567
HE'S THE BEST DARN
WATCH CAT IN THE WORLD.

04:35.567 --> 04:38.903
BESIDES, I KNOW
THAT KARATE STUFF.

04:38.903 --> 04:40.238
HYAH!

04:40.238 --> 04:41.239
HO!

04:41.239 --> 04:42.490
HII!

04:42.490 --> 04:44.200
HEE HEE HEE!

04:44.200 --> 04:45.827
[ROWR]

04:45.827 --> 04:47.328
SORRY, KITTY.

04:47.328 --> 04:49.414
NOW DO YOU BELIEVE ME, SON?

04:49.414 --> 04:52.250
WELL...YAAH!

04:52.250 --> 04:56.588
SAY, NEIGHBOR,
NOTICED YOUR WINDOW
WAS LEFT OPEN.

04:56.588 --> 04:58.548
NOT TOO SAFE,
YOU KNOW.

04:58.548 --> 05:01.843
OH, THANKS, PETEY. I WAS
JUST ABOUT TO LOCK IT.

05:01.843 --> 05:06.681
YEP. CAN'T BE TOO CAREFUL
WITH BURGLARS ABOUT.

05:06.681 --> 05:09.351
SEE? EVEN PETE'S
LOOKING OUT FOR US.

05:09.351 --> 05:11.561
AAH!

05:11.561 --> 05:14.272
SHUCKS, MAX.
WHEN I WAS A KID,

05:14.272 --> 05:16.941
I WAS SCARED OF BURGLARS,
TOO. AH-HYUCK!

05:16.941 --> 05:19.361
ONCE I SMEARED BUTTER
ALL OVER THE STAIRS.

05:19.361 --> 05:20.570
WHAT DID YOU CATCH?

05:20.570 --> 05:23.239
A COLD. I SLID
OUT THE FRONT DOOR

05:23.239 --> 05:25.742
AND LANDED IN
A SNOW BANK. AH-HYUCK!

05:25.742 --> 05:26.910
GOOD NIGHT, SON.

05:26.910 --> 05:29.287
YEAH. GOOD NIGHT.

05:35.877 --> 05:38.296
[BELL RINGS]

05:39.881 --> 05:41.633
WHAT'S SHAKIN',
MAD MAX?

05:41.633 --> 05:44.386
LISTEN, WHILE YOU'RE
SLEEPING TONIGHT,

05:44.386 --> 05:46.054
CAN YOU KEEP AN EYE
ON OUR HOUSE?

05:46.054 --> 05:48.306
YEAH. NO PROBLEM.

05:48.306 --> 05:51.226
I LOVE SLEEPING
LIKE A ZOMBIE.

05:51.226 --> 05:53.269
HA HA HA!
GOOD NIGHT, MAN.

05:56.606 --> 05:58.483
[YAWNS]

06:03.321 --> 06:04.572
OW!

06:06.157 --> 06:08.785
AH-HYUCK!
BEEN LOOKING FOR THAT.

06:08.785 --> 06:09.828
[CLATTER]
[GASP]

06:09.828 --> 06:11.162
WAFFLES,
DID YOU HEAR THAT?

06:15.291 --> 06:17.669
GAWRSH! I FORGOT
TO TUCK MAX IN.

06:20.422 --> 06:21.923
DOGGONE DOOR.

06:21.923 --> 06:23.925
SOMEONE'S TRYING
TO GET IN.

06:23.925 --> 06:25.885
[GRUNTING]

06:29.264 --> 06:31.933
[YAWN]

06:31.933 --> 06:33.184
HE'S HERE!

06:33.184 --> 06:34.436
[MEOW]

06:39.357 --> 06:41.151
OW!

06:41.151 --> 06:42.485
DAD!

06:44.029 --> 06:45.864
OH, NO, DAD.
I'M REALLY SORRY.

06:45.864 --> 06:47.532
I'M REALLY SORRY. WAKE UP.
PLEASE, PLEASE WAKE UP.

06:47.532 --> 06:49.868
I WANT TO THANK THE MEMBERS
OF THE ACADEMY

06:49.868 --> 06:52.037
FOR THIS AWARD. HYUCK!

06:53.163 --> 06:55.081
WOW! WHAT HAPPENED?

06:55.081 --> 06:58.835
UM, I--I THOUGHT
YOU WERE A BURGLAR.

06:58.835 --> 07:01.379
YOU REALLY
GOT TO CALM DOWN, SON.

07:01.379 --> 07:02.881
IT'S TOUGH ON MY SHINS.

07:02.881 --> 07:07.135
HA HA. OKAY, DAD.
I'M FINE NOW.

07:08.178 --> 07:09.512
I LOVE YOU, SON.

07:09.512 --> 07:11.056
NOW GO TO SLEEP.

07:11.056 --> 07:12.474
LOVE YOU, TOO.

07:12.474 --> 07:15.643
DON'T WORRY.
I'LL ALWAYS BE HERE

07:15.643 --> 07:17.145
TO PROTECT YOU.

07:17.145 --> 07:18.563
WHOA!

07:20.523 --> 07:22.025
DIDN'T HURT.

07:23.735 --> 07:26.738
DAD'S RIGHT.
I'M BEING A JERK.

07:26.738 --> 07:28.698
I'LL LISTEN TO SOME MUSIC.

07:30.533 --> 07:32.911
MY RADIO! IT'S GONE!

07:32.911 --> 07:35.413
THERE REALLY IS A BURGLAR!

07:43.171 --> 07:44.673
OHH...

07:44.673 --> 07:45.924
GOOD LOOK ON YOU.

07:45.924 --> 07:47.842
I DIDN'T SLEEP A WINK.

07:47.842 --> 07:50.345
STAY UP FOR THE
"TWILIGHT ZONE" MARATHON?

07:51.554 --> 07:53.932
I AM THE "TWILIGHT ZONE."

07:53.932 --> 07:56.017
I WAS ROBBED, PJ.

07:56.017 --> 07:57.852
CRUSTY!

07:57.852 --> 08:01.064
YEAH. SOMEONE BROKE
INTO MY ROOM LAST NIGHT.

08:01.064 --> 08:03.108
MUST HAVE BEEN 10 FEET TALL.

08:03.108 --> 08:06.027
I ALMOST CAUGHT HIM,
BUT HE SWIPED MY RADIO.

08:06.027 --> 08:09.531
GEEZ!
FIRST MY GLOVE
AND NOW THIS.

08:09.531 --> 08:11.282
LOOKS LIKE I WAS RIGHT.

08:11.282 --> 08:14.869
YOU WERE NUMBER FOUR
AFTER ALL.

08:14.869 --> 08:16.871
YEAH. WE'RE JUST NOT SAFE.

08:16.871 --> 08:18.873
NOW I'LL NEVER GET ANY SLEEP.

08:18.873 --> 08:20.333
YOU GOT TO DO SOMETHING.

08:20.333 --> 08:21.543
LIKE WHAT?

08:21.543 --> 08:22.919
UH,

08:22.919 --> 08:25.714
THE ANSWER'S JUST
AS SIMPLE AS YOU ARE.

08:27.382 --> 08:29.342
GET A SECURITY SYSTEM.

08:31.011 --> 08:32.846
THAT'S EXACTLY
WHAT WE NEED.

08:32.846 --> 08:34.472
HA HA HA HA!

08:34.472 --> 08:36.474
THIS I GOT TO SEE.

08:38.226 --> 08:39.936
DAD! DAD!

08:39.936 --> 08:41.396
WHOA! OW!

08:41.396 --> 08:45.150
SORRY, MR. G, BUT MAXIE
HAS A RIGHTEOUS IDEA.

08:45.150 --> 08:47.152
OH, YEAH? WHAT IS IT?

08:47.152 --> 08:49.446
A SECURITY SYSTEM
FOR THE HOUSE.

08:49.446 --> 08:51.656
A WHAT?
[PJ] A BURGLAR ALARM.

08:51.656 --> 08:54.451
LOOK, MAX, I THOUGHT
WE SETTLED THIS.

08:54.451 --> 08:55.493
BUT, DAD...

08:57.120 --> 08:59.497
AS LONG AS YOUR DAD
IS ON THE ALERT,

08:59.497 --> 09:01.666
WE'RE NOT GETTING
ANY BURGLAR ALARM.

09:10.008 --> 09:13.470
SO, UH, HOW'D
IT GO, FELLAS?

09:13.470 --> 09:14.929
CRASHED AND BURNED.

09:14.929 --> 09:16.931
DAD THINKS
WE'RE ALREADY SAFE.

09:16.931 --> 09:19.601
YEP. SOME FOLKS
WON'T DO ANYTHING

09:19.601 --> 09:21.936
TILL IT'S TOO LATE.

09:21.936 --> 09:25.982
I'D SAY THAT GUY
NEEDS TO BE ROBBED.

09:25.982 --> 09:29.319
MR. P, THAT'S IT.
WE'LL HAVE A BURGLARY.

09:29.319 --> 09:33.198
YEAH, BUT, MAX, HOW DO YOU KNOW
WHEN A BURGLAR'S GONNA BURGLE?

09:33.198 --> 09:37.327
OH, IT'LL HAPPEN MUCH
SOONER THAN YOU THINK.

09:41.331 --> 09:42.832
[SNORING]

09:58.682 --> 10:00.308
HEE HEE HEE HEE!

10:03.395 --> 10:05.563
[ROOSTER CROWS]

10:09.651 --> 10:12.529
OOH...
MAN, AM I BEAT.

10:28.586 --> 10:30.422
[HUMMING]

10:36.052 --> 10:37.178
OHH...

10:37.178 --> 10:39.347
NEED SOME COFFEE.

10:39.347 --> 10:41.182
THIS'LL WAKE ME UP.

10:43.018 --> 10:44.602
STRONG STUFF.

10:44.602 --> 10:45.729
WHAT?

10:45.729 --> 10:48.398
I'VE BEEN ROBBED! ROBBED!

10:48.398 --> 10:50.567
HELP! HELP! THIEVES!

10:50.567 --> 10:52.402
HA HA HA HA HA!

10:52.402 --> 10:53.570
LOOK AT THAT!

10:53.570 --> 10:55.405
ROBBERS! BURGLARS!
CROOKS!

10:55.405 --> 10:58.408
HA HA HA!
YOU TELL THEM, GOOF!

10:58.408 --> 11:00.076
GET THE MARINES!
GET THE POLICE!

11:00.076 --> 11:02.120
GET THE NUMBER FOR 911!

11:02.120 --> 11:03.496
[LAUGHTER]

11:03.496 --> 11:04.664
[PJ]
CHECK IT OUT.

11:05.874 --> 11:07.375
HO HO HO HO!

11:07.375 --> 11:08.626
[MAX]
AH, DAD.

11:08.626 --> 11:10.211
HA HA!

11:10.211 --> 11:11.379
HIYA, POP.

11:11.379 --> 11:12.630
WHAT'S GOING ON?

11:12.630 --> 11:15.133
HEY! THAT'S OUR
MISSING STUFF.

11:15.133 --> 11:17.302
YEAH. WE STOLE IT.

11:17.302 --> 11:20.472
HA HA. HOPE YOU'RE
NOT SORE, MR. G.

11:20.472 --> 11:22.557
I DON'T THINK
THAT'S VERY FUNNY.

11:22.557 --> 11:25.977
THAT'S THE POINT, DAD.
BEING RIPPED OFF ISN'T FUNNY.

11:25.977 --> 11:29.481
GAWRSH. MAYBE I'M NOT
AS ALERT AS I THOUGHT.

11:29.481 --> 11:31.483
SO CAN WE GET
A SECURITY SYSTEM?

11:31.483 --> 11:32.484
YOU BET.

11:32.484 --> 11:34.319
WAY COOL!

11:34.319 --> 11:36.321
AND WE'LL MAKE IT
OURSELVES.

11:36.321 --> 11:39.657
BUT, DAD, DON'T YOU WANT ONE
OF THOSE PROFESSIONAL JOBS

11:39.657 --> 11:43.161
WITH THE SENSORS AND BELLS
AND LASERS AND MISSILES?

11:43.161 --> 11:44.579
NOPE. TOO EXPENSIVE.

11:44.579 --> 11:46.206
OURS WILL BE
JUST AS SNAZZY.

11:46.206 --> 11:48.708
YOU WATCH. WE'LL START
AS SOON AS YOU MOVE

11:48.708 --> 11:50.669
ALL THIS STUFF
BACK IN THE HOUSE.

11:53.213 --> 11:55.507
YOU SURE THIS STUFF
IS GONNA WORK?

11:55.507 --> 11:58.593
HECK, YEAH.
ANY CROOK DUMB ENOUGH
TO WALK THROUGH HERE

11:58.593 --> 12:00.428
IS IN FOR A BIG SURPRISE.

12:00.428 --> 12:02.597
WHOOPS. FORGOT MY SAW.

12:02.597 --> 12:04.641
WHOOPS! WHOA!

12:08.812 --> 12:10.772
BOY, FOR SOMETHING
SO STUPID,

12:10.772 --> 12:13.358
THAT SURE SMARTS. AH-HYUCK!

12:15.151 --> 12:16.653
[SAW BUZZES]

12:16.653 --> 12:18.863
[HAMMER POUNDS]

12:21.616 --> 12:23.827
PJ, WHAT'S ALL THAT RACKET?

12:23.827 --> 12:27.163
MR. G AND MAX ARE BUILDING
THEIR OWN SECURITY SYSTEM.

12:27.163 --> 12:29.207
WHY, THOSE ROCKET SCIENTISTS

12:29.207 --> 12:31.793
ARE PESTERING
MY PEACE AND QUIET!

12:33.586 --> 12:35.422
BURGLAR ALARMS. HAH!

12:35.422 --> 12:37.340
WHAT A BUNCH
OF SCAREDY-GOOFS.

12:37.340 --> 12:38.758
THEY GOT A LOT OF NERVE.

12:38.758 --> 12:41.094
AAH! MY BENCH SAW!

12:49.728 --> 12:51.479
[LAUGHING]

12:51.479 --> 12:54.983
QUICK! CALL THE FBI!
CALL THE CIA! CALL THE PTA!

12:54.983 --> 12:56.985
WHAT'S WRONG,
TINSEL TUSH?

12:56.985 --> 13:02.657
MY NEW $2,000-PLUS-TAX
BENCH SAW--GONE!

13:02.657 --> 13:06.369
I NEED SECURITY!

13:06.369 --> 13:09.914
YES, SIR, PETE, YOU'VE
MADE A WISE CHOICE.

13:09.914 --> 13:12.375
THIS IS THE WORLD'S
FINEST SECURITY SYSTEM,

13:12.375 --> 13:15.045
OR MY NAME'S NOT
BATTLIN' BIFF BOFFO.

13:15.045 --> 13:16.796
IF SOME DIRTBAG MANAGES

13:16.796 --> 13:19.049
TO SURVIVE THE FENCE
AND THE LASER BEAMS,

13:19.049 --> 13:21.968
THIS 50-GAUGE STEEL
WILL KEEP HIM OUT.

13:21.968 --> 13:24.721
HMM, STYLISH, TOO.

13:24.721 --> 13:26.765
DON'T YOU THINK
SO, SWEETUMS?

13:26.765 --> 13:28.099
HOW MUCH?

13:29.267 --> 13:31.561
ONLY, UH, 30,000.

13:34.564 --> 13:37.233
ARE YOU NUTS?
WE DON'T NEED ALL THIS.

13:37.233 --> 13:40.028
IT'S LIKE
SWATTING MOSQUITOES
WITH A BAZOOKA.

13:40.028 --> 13:41.404
NO, MA'AM.

13:41.404 --> 13:43.782
WE SAVE THE BAZOOKA
FOR THE SALESMEN.

13:43.782 --> 13:45.533
WITH A SINGLE BUTTON,

13:45.533 --> 13:47.535
INTRUDERS ARE
YESTERDAY'S HASH.

13:52.707 --> 13:57.003
OOH. NOW THAT'S FIREPOWER.

13:57.003 --> 13:59.923
AND THE BEST PART--
IT'S FULLY AUTOMATIC.

13:59.923 --> 14:02.884
WELL, GOTTA CONTINUE
MY WAR ON CRIME.

14:02.884 --> 14:04.594
SO LONG, TROOPS.

14:04.594 --> 14:06.763
LET'S MOVE OUT, MEN!

14:06.763 --> 14:10.100
HUT-2, HUT-2,
HUT-2, HUT-2.

14:10.100 --> 14:11.976
HUT-2, HUT-2...

14:14.396 --> 14:16.314
COOL!

14:16.314 --> 14:18.316
[SNORING]

14:18.316 --> 14:20.276
DAD! DAD!

14:20.276 --> 14:23.113
HAVE YOU SEEN HOW SAFE
PETE'S HOUSE IS?

14:23.113 --> 14:26.741
NOPE. I WORE MYSELF OUT
MAKING US SAFE.

14:26.741 --> 14:28.785
LOOKS PRETTY GOOD,
DON'T IT?

14:28.785 --> 14:30.745
OH. YEAH, DAD,
REAL SNAZZY.

14:30.745 --> 14:32.747
CAN I SLEEP OVER
PJ's TONIGHT?

14:32.747 --> 14:35.291
DON'T YOU WANT
TO TEST OUT THE NEW--

14:35.291 --> 14:36.793
THANKS, DAD. BYE.

14:36.793 --> 14:40.839
GEE, KITTY, GUESS IT'S
JUST YOU AND ME NOW.

14:40.839 --> 14:44.718
TELL YOU WHAT. I'LL TAKE
THE FIRST WATCH TONIGHT.

14:44.718 --> 14:46.177
[SNORING]

14:47.721 --> 14:50.932
OKAY. REST EASY.

14:50.932 --> 14:53.101
OL' GOOFY'S ON THE JOB.

15:03.486 --> 15:07.449
OH, YEAH. I REALLY
FEEL SAFE OVER HERE.

15:07.449 --> 15:11.327
LOOKS LIKE TONIGHT I'M
FINALLY GONNA GET SOME SLEEP.

15:12.871 --> 15:15.457
[BIFF]
GOOD. EVERYONE'S ASLEEP.

15:15.457 --> 15:17.917
FOLLOW ME, YOU DIM BULBS.

15:17.917 --> 15:19.294
[BANG]

15:19.294 --> 15:20.879
WHAT WAS THAT?

15:31.973 --> 15:35.060
HEH HEH HEH!
I LOVE THIS PART.

15:35.060 --> 15:37.729
FIRST WE SELL 'EM,
THEN WE ROB 'EM.

15:40.190 --> 15:41.358
[DOOR UNLOCKS]

15:43.026 --> 15:44.319
BURGLARS!

15:51.201 --> 15:53.536
OKAY, BOYS,
STRIP THE JOINT.

15:57.999 --> 16:01.252
WAIT. DON'T YOU WANT
THE VAN KEYS?

16:01.252 --> 16:03.838
UH, PUT 'EM
IN MY POCKET, OKAY?

16:04.881 --> 16:06.508
GOTTA STOP THEIR GETAWAY.

16:16.017 --> 16:17.394
[CRASH]

16:17.394 --> 16:19.938
HOT DOG! BURGLARS!

16:22.607 --> 16:25.360
HOLD IT RIGHT THERE, BOZO!

16:30.115 --> 16:31.908
GOTTA TELL DAD.

16:36.913 --> 16:39.791
I--WAIT. I CAN'T--
UH-OH...

16:39.791 --> 16:41.126
GRRR!

16:41.126 --> 16:43.837
GIVE ME THEM KEYS.

16:45.255 --> 16:47.048
BOSS!

16:47.048 --> 16:49.801
BOSS! BOSS!
HELP!

16:49.801 --> 16:51.469
BOSS, COME HERE!

16:51.469 --> 16:53.138
HE'S GOT OUR KEYS.

17:03.565 --> 17:07.902
PJ! SOMEBODY! HELP!

17:07.902 --> 17:09.320
MAX!

17:11.656 --> 17:13.575
HELP!

17:13.575 --> 17:16.494
OHH! TRAPPED!
I GOTTA HELP MAX!

17:21.374 --> 17:23.960
OH, THESE STUPID
SAFETY SCISSORS.

17:28.882 --> 17:30.425
AAH!

17:35.096 --> 17:36.765
DAD! DAD!

17:37.974 --> 17:39.267
DAD, WAKE UP!

17:39.267 --> 17:40.685
DAD?

17:43.772 --> 17:45.690
MURRAY, YOU TAKE
THE BASEMENT.

17:45.690 --> 17:46.983
MOOSE, FOLLOW ME.

17:50.278 --> 17:53.156
HEY, THIS WAS EASY.

17:53.156 --> 17:54.699
[ALARM BUZZES]
UH-OH.

18:00.997 --> 18:02.665
WHOA!

18:02.665 --> 18:05.126
WHOA-AAH!

18:05.126 --> 18:06.878
DAD, WHERE ARE YOU?

18:06.878 --> 18:09.005
OKAY, KID,
HAND OVER THOSE KEYS,

18:09.005 --> 18:12.592
OR I'LL MUSH YOU
LIKE BANANA FRITTERS.

18:14.761 --> 18:16.304
OH!

18:18.390 --> 18:21.476
HUH! WHAT DO YA KNOW?
IT REALLY WORKS.

18:22.977 --> 18:24.396
[GOOFY, WAFFLES SNORING]

18:27.023 --> 18:28.149
DAD!

18:29.693 --> 18:31.903
DAD, WAKE UP!

18:31.903 --> 18:33.988
GET THAT PIPSQUEAK!

18:35.407 --> 18:36.574
DAD'S STAIRBLASTER.

18:38.868 --> 18:40.829
WHOA!

18:40.829 --> 18:42.956
IT'S LAUNDRY TIME.

18:48.378 --> 18:50.463
AAH!

19:01.766 --> 19:03.393
GOTCHA!
OH!

19:05.687 --> 19:07.397
[GRUNTING]

19:07.397 --> 19:08.565
OH, BOY!

19:08.565 --> 19:10.066
[SNORT]

19:13.695 --> 19:16.406
ONE GIANT BUTT FOR MOOSEKIND.

19:21.953 --> 19:24.664
[RING]

19:33.673 --> 19:34.841
OH!

19:34.841 --> 19:37.093
HELP!

19:38.720 --> 19:39.971
FOR THE LAST TIME--

19:41.222 --> 19:43.558
GIVE ME THOSE KEYS!

20:10.752 --> 20:13.880
WHAT'S THE MATTER?
GETTIN' TIRED?

20:13.880 --> 20:17.717
THE KEYS, KID.
HAND THEM OVER
REAL NICE.

20:17.717 --> 20:20.553
I'M WILLING TO DISCUSS IT.

20:20.553 --> 20:23.306
YOU'RE GONNA BE RAVIOLI!

20:23.306 --> 20:24.766
SORRY. CHANGED MY MIND.

20:30.814 --> 20:32.357
ALL RIGHT, DAD!

20:46.121 --> 20:48.707
FORGET THE KEYS.
FORGET THE LOOT.

20:48.707 --> 20:51.292
I JUST WANT OUT!

20:52.419 --> 20:53.670
NO!

20:53.670 --> 20:54.921
IT CAN'T BE.

20:54.921 --> 20:56.756
OH! OH! OH! AAH!

20:58.550 --> 21:00.719
JUST HAD A CHAT
WITH THE POLICE.

21:00.719 --> 21:04.472
LET US OUT! LET US OUT!

21:15.233 --> 21:17.569
[SIREN]

21:20.071 --> 21:21.072
[POP]

21:21.072 --> 21:22.157
[MEOW]

21:22.157 --> 21:24.200
HUH? WHAT? HEY!

21:28.079 --> 21:29.956
HEY, RIP VAN WINKLE,

21:29.956 --> 21:31.249
YOU MISSED
ALL THE EXCITEMENT.

21:31.249 --> 21:33.501
I DID?
IT WAS FANTASTIC.

21:33.501 --> 21:35.587
YOUR SECURITY SYSTEM
WORKED GREAT.

21:35.587 --> 21:38.173
SEE? TOLD YOU
YOU DIDN'T HAVE TO WORRY

21:38.173 --> 21:40.467
WITH YOUR OLD DAD AROUND.

21:40.467 --> 21:43.636
WHAT SAY WE GET
SOME SHUT-EYE?

21:43.636 --> 21:46.848
[YAWN]
YEAH. I'M POOPED.

21:46.848 --> 21:48.224
UH-OH.

21:48.224 --> 21:51.061
HEY, LET ME IN!
LET ME IN!

21:53.730 --> 21:57.275
HEY, LET ME OUT!
LET ME OUT!

21:58.777 --> 22:01.237
HEE HEE HEE HA HA HA!
